*Storage (Page 3 of 6)*

=== Persistent Per-User Storage ===
Storage is scoped by user ID. Your keys are separate from other users.

=== Save ===
`(store "key" value)`
Example: `(store "score" 42)`

=== Read ===
`(read "key")`
Returns `nil` when key is missing.

=== Delete ===
`(delete "key")`
Returns `true` if deleted, `false` if key did not exist.

=== Slash Helpers ===
`/s7 store` - List your keys
`/s7 store clear` - Delete all your stored keys

Use `/s7 help 4` for interactive UI.
